    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=608106698237805466&sectionId=608114683991294550)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHXN6KqF2W_text","label":"ggHXN6KqF2W_text","default":"<p>When Sarah Stopped Being Sarah</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyuj3m3c4O_text","label":"ggyuj3m3c4O_text","default":"<p>Sarah Whitfield used to be the kind of woman who ran the room — sharp, funny, managed a 15-person marketing team, trained for half-marathons, never missed a school event. But by 45, something shifted. And it never shifted back.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9dt0zok7__text","label":"gg9dt0zok7__text","default":"<p>The symptoms arrived like uninvited guests that refused to leave:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj06GNzH3Q_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggj06GNzH3Q_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggopjhTuGvm_text","label":"ggopjhTuGvm_text","default":"<p>❌ Bloating so severe she looked six months pregnant by 2 PM every day</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnCNIjY22n_text","label":"ggnCNIjY22n_text","default":"<p>❌ 3 AM wake-ups — every single night, like clockwork</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZpXN4lA7p_text","label":"ggZpXN4lA7p_text","default":"<p>❌ Exhaustion that eight hours of sleep couldn't touch</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkUxnOY1xy_text","label":"ggkUxnOY1xy_text","default":"<p>❌ Brain fog so thick she'd forget words mid-sentence</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbGZHnqM74_text","label":"ggbGZHnqM74_text","default":"<p>❌ Sugar cravings at exactly the same time every afternoon</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbfQTmkbn-_text","label":"ggbfQTmkbn-_text","default":"<p>❌ Skin tags appearing on her neck</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSG32grfwV_text","label":"ggSG32grfwV_text","default":"<p>❌ Dry, itchy patches no cream could fix</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqHX3BDP0h_text","label":"ggqHX3BDP0h_text","default":"<p>❌ Teeth grinding that cracked a molar</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiqE_SBQZP_text","label":"ggiqE_SBQZP_text","default":"<p>❌ Feeling \"crawly\" sensations under her skin at night</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqo9rfLJ3B_text","label":"ggqo9rfLJ3B_text","default":"<p>The medical carousel started spinning. Each symptom earned a new specialist, a new test, a new label — and a new prescription.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEpRg8mXN1_text","label":"ggEpRg8mXN1_text","default":"<p><i>\"Middle-age hormones. Happens to most women. Try probiotics.</i>\" — Sarah's primary care physician</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrCD5lKcd4_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggrCD5lKcd4_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggd_M28mbfM_text","label":"ggd_M28mbfM_text","default":"<p>$89 probiotics did nothing. Neither did digestive enzymes. Neither did the elimination diets that slowly stripped every joy from eating. The gastroenterologist's verdict: \"IBS. Manage your stress. Eat more fiber.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPdnArLvhG_text","label":"ggPdnArLvhG_text","default":"<p>Fiber made it worse. By year two, Sarah's medicine cabinet looked like a pharmacy:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdl6Kslfu2_text","label":"ggdl6Kslfu2_text","default":"<p>1. Dicyclomine (IBS cramping)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLOtGJQTjR_text","label":"ggLOtGJQTjR_text","default":"<p>2. Omeprazole (acid reflux)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7sLIn1wnL_text","label":"gg7sLIn1wnL_text","default":"<p>3. Lexapro (\"anxiety\")</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTzoKU1z18_text","label":"ggTzoKU1z18_text","default":"<p>4. Hydroxyzine (sleep)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggU9xzpND8D_text","label":"ggU9xzpND8D_text","default":"<p>5. Miralax (constipation from the other meds)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguGzhmjnWF_text","label":"gguGzhmjnWF_text","default":"<p>6. Metamucil (fiber — the thing making it worse)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggB5I-3tNac_text","label":"ggB5I-3tNac_text","default":"<p>7. OTC Ibuprofen (headaches from the brain fog)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggM9Ybm7vZi_text","label":"ggM9Ybm7vZi_text","default":"<p><i>\"They had a pill for every symptom. But not one doctor ever asked why I was having all of them at the same time.\" — </i>Sarah Whitfield</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJhmS1lkq8_text","label":"ggJhmS1lkq8_text","default":"<p>The breaking point came on a Tuesday night. Sarah sat on the edge of the bed, crying, and said five words that broke Gary's heart:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnz7-QQmxU_text","label":"ggnz7-QQmxU_text","default":"<p><i>\"I'm broken. What's wrong with me?\"</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXwLwgmPXK_text","label":"ggXwLwgmPXK_text","default":"<p>Before finding the answer, the Whitfield’s spent:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbs7JmAssX_text","label":"ggbs7JmAssX_text","default":"<p>⚠️ $3,200 on colonoscopy (\"just inflammation\")</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1XAPWYMYi_text","label":"gg1XAPWYMYi_text","default":"<p>⚠️ $2,800 on food sensitivity panels (\"avoid gluten and dairy\")</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNlsCqdur4_text","label":"ggNlsCqdur4_text","default":"<p>⚠️ $4,200 on functional medicine consultations</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKRwc6O5IK_text","label":"ggKRwc6O5IK_text","default":"<p>⚠️ $9,600 on IBS medications over 2 years</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnFBvleaj9_text","label":"ggnFBvleaj9_text","default":"<p>⚠️ $1,800 on probiotics and digestive enzymes</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyvaFdF51S_text","label":"ggyvaFdF51S_text","default":"<p>⚠️ $1,400 on elimination diet coaching</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggA9GWxHXdn_text","label":"ggA9GWxHXdn_text","default":"<p><i>\"We spent twenty-three thousand dollars to be told nothing was wrong. The answer cost us forty-four dollars.\" — </i>Gary Whitfield</p>"}],
